window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Protect the women. Take the throne.</p> <p>Awaking on the shores of a primitive world, David discovers a remote village populated almost entirely by women.</p> <p>Powerful witches have killed the men, destroying their tribal society. The women have little defense against the wild beasts and opportunistic goblin slavers who roam their forests.</p> <p>With a mysterious new power raging in his muscles, David becomes their guardian, provider, and leader. Beautiful women flock to him, believing he was sent by a sky god to protect them.</p>"; 
